casebody.data:
Lorain County Bar Association v. Parobek.

[Cite as Lorain Cty. Bar Assn. v. Parobek (1998), 83 Ohio St.3d 325.]

(No. 98-829 Submitted June 10, 1998 Decided September 30, 1998.) *326Stephen P. Bond, for relator. Craig Wright, for respondent. Per Curiam.

We adopt the findings, conclusion, and recommendation of the board. Respondent is hereby publicly reprimanded. Costs taxed to respondent.

Judgment accordingly.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur.
